## Third-Party Components

This software bundles and/or installs the following third-party components:

### Git for Windows
- License: GPL v2
- Website: https://git-scm.com/
- Note: Bundled installer, not modified

### Node.js
- License: MIT
- Website: https://nodejs.org/
- Note: Bundled installer, not modified

### WSL (Windows Subsystem for Linux)
- License: Microsoft Software License
- Provider: Microsoft Corporation
- Note: Downloaded from Microsoft during installation

### Ubuntu
- License: Various open source licenses
- Provider: Canonical Ltd.
- Website: https://ubuntu.com/
- Note: Downloaded from Microsoft Store during installation

### Konsole
- License: GPL v2
- Provider: KDE Project
- Website: https://konsole.kde.org/
- Note: Installed via apt package manager

### Claude Code
- License: Proprietary
- Provider: Anthropic
- Website: https://claude.com/claude-code
- Note: Installed via npm, requires Anthropic API key

### Hebrew Fonts
- Noto Sans Mono: SIL Open Font License 1.1
- DejaVu Sans Mono: MIT-style license
- Culmus (optional): GPL
- SIL Ezra (optional): SIL Open Font License

---

## Disclaimer

This is an installer/configuration package for Claude Code with Hebrew RTL support.
It does not modify or redistribute Claude Code itself.

Claude Code is a proprietary product of Anthropic and requires a valid API key.
See https://console.anthropic.com for API access.
